%h1 Uploads
%p.description Uploads are a place to store your important documents like contracts and client proposals. Uploads that you make public can be shared directly with your clients.

- if @uploads.blank?
  %p You haven't uploaded any files yet.
-else
  %table
    %tr
      %th Title
      %th Category
      %th
      %th
      %th

    - @uploads.each do |upload|
      %tr
        %td= upload.title
        %td= upload.category
        %td= link_to 'Show', upload
        %td= link_to 'Edit', edit_upload_path(upload)
        %td= link_to 'Destroy', upload_path(upload), :confirm => 'Are you sure?', :method => :delete

  %br

= link_to 'New Upload', new_upload_path, :class => 'button'
